DROP EXTERNAL TABLE DIM_MFR;

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE DIM_MFR (
	[MFRHorse] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRVehicleStatus] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRBranch] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRModel] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFREquipment] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRChassisNumber] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRVehicleColour] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFREngineNumber] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRApplication] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRDivision] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRRecommendedTyreSize] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRAlternativeTyreSize] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRDepotCode] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRExpiryDateOnLicence] datetime2(7),
	[MFRLicenceFee] numeric(19,6),
	[MFRGrossVehicleMass] numeric(19,6),
	[MFRTareWeight] numeric(19,6),
	[MFRPayload] numeric(19,6),
	[MFRPeopleCarrier] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRTotalNoOfTyres] int,
	[MFRNoOfSteeringAxleTyres] int,
	[MFRNoOfRearAxleTyres] int,
	[MFRExternalBodyLength_M] numeric(19,6),
	[MFRFleetNo] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRExternalBodyWidth_M] numeric(19,6),
	[MFRExternalBodyHeight_M] numeric(19,6),
	[MFRInternalBodyLength_M] numeric(19,6),
	[MFRInternalBodyWidth_M] numeric(19,6),
	[MFRInternalBodyHeight_M] numeric(19,6),
	[MFRInternalVolumetricCapacity] numeric(19,6),
	[MFRMakeOfBody] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRAvailbilityForAdvertising] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRAdvertisingOrSignwritingOn] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRFrameworkInstalledForFlexiMount] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRCcClass/TypeOfVehicle] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRDiesel/Petrol] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRTankCapacity] int,
	[MFRKMRangeOnFullTankFuel] numeric(19,6),
	[MFRTargetConsumption] numeric(19,6),
	[MFRKMs/Litre] numeric(19,6),
	[MFREngineProtection/IdleRevs] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFROriginalFinanceCompany] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRContractNumber] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRRegNo] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRContractStartDate] datetime2(7),
	[MFRContractEndDate] datetime2(7),
	[MFRFirstInstalmentDate] datetime2(7),
	[MFRPreviousOwnershipOfVehicle] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRFleetHaulNumber] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFROldRegNo] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRETollClass] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRAssetStatus] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRYearModel] int,
	[MFRMake] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRSeries] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRPTName] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRAssetCode] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRVehicleFinanced] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRHasRegChanged] nvarchar(4000),
	[MFRBackDoorWidth] numeric(19,6),
	[MFRBackDoorHeight] numeric(19,6)
	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'DataLake/Structured/Dimensions/DIM_MFR.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO



SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.DIM_MFR
GO
